PREFIX CHEBI: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_>


            SELECT ?ec_readable (COUNT(DISTINCT ?protein) AS ?count)
WHERE {
    ?protein a up:Protein ;
            up:enzyme ?enzyme .
    ?enzyme rdfs:subClassOf ?ec .
    BIND(REPLACE(STR(?ec), "http://purl.uniprot.org/ec/", "") AS ?ec_readable)
    FILTER(REGEX(?ec_readable, "^[1-7]\\.-\\.-\\.-$"))
}
GROUP BY ?ec_readable
ORDER BY DESC(?count)

            LIMIT 20
